title: NPLC Podcast A New Hope
description: The blood moon has risen over, and the dark side has created a disturbance within the republic. We here at NPLC, are not going down without a fight. We are now broadcasting from an undisclosed linux box, somewhere from the north. Join John-Douglas, commonly known as Sam, and Mr. Bob on our new independent venue. We are gearing up, and are going to bring forth an onslaught of truthiness!
